Mongolian input table for IBus
==============================

Install
-------

Run install.sh script. Install script assumes you have permission to /usr/share/ibus-table. If you can't find some keys, look in mongolian.txt. 

Customizing
-----------

If you want to customize mapping table, 
 - Open mongolian.txt and do changes. 
 - Then run compile.sh. 
 - If compiling succeeds, run install.sh
 - Restart idus-daemon. 
Or you could just run deploy.sh to compile and install.

Дараа нь ингээд монголоор бичих болно. 

